124 (i) The commissioner shall promulgate rules and regulations necessary to implement and
125 administer the provisions of this Code section."
126 SECTION 2.
127 This Act shall become effective on January 1, 2026, and shall be applicable to taxable years
128 beginning on or after such date.
129 SECTION 3.
130 All laws and parts of laws in conflict with this Act are repealed.
